      [
        "It’s no secret that I’m a huge fan of videogames…"
      ],
      [
        "I mean, my career is videogame related! "
      ],
      [
        "But to be honest, they bring huge comfort to me. In any bad day, or bad moment,"
      ],
      [
        "I played and played until I forgot what had me bummed out in the beginning. "
      ],
      [
        "I also enjoy fantasizing and making up scenarios and characters."
      ],
      [
        "I think that someday, I could be able to make a videogame so good that"
      ],
      [
        "it will help other little kids that are like me to help them overcome every bad moment in life that they have…"
      ],
      [
        "I guess that has always been my dream. "
      ]
